      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a resident of Haryana and possess a valid Parivar Pehchan Patra (PPP).\n1. The applicant must submit an undertaking in the DPR to bear all operational, maintenance, and post-construction management costs, and to ensure the continuous functioning of the ice plant/cold storage.\n1. The applicant must note that central assistance will be provided as per the actual cost, subject to the ceiling limits under relevant PMMSY sub-components.\n1. The applicant must ensure that the ice produced is supplied to fishers and fish farmers at an affordable price.\n1. The applicant must either own the project land or hold it on a long-term registered lease of at least 10 years to be eligible.\n\n",
